{"title":"De Rosa 70 is a Much-Lighter Pininfarina-designed Aero Road Bike","link":"https://bikerumor.com/de-rosa-70-is-a-much-lighter-pininfarina-designed-aero-road-bike/","date":1683044910000,"content":"<p>Celebrating seventy years of crafting premium Italian road bikes, De Rosa is back with the all-new lightweight carbon 70 aero road bike shaped by renowned racing design firm Pininfarina and almost 1/4 lighter than its predecessor! Officially dubbed the Settanta – <em>seventy</em> in Italian – they are calling this anniversary road ride “<em>the most advanced De Rosa bike of all time</em>“.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>De Rosa 70 lightweight aero road bike, by Pininfarina designs</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-Pininfarina-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_complete.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-Pininfarina-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_complete-800x480.jpg\" alt=\"De Rosa 70 Settanta lightweight carbon aero road bike, designed by Pininfarina, complete\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-Pininfarina-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_complete-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-Pininfarina-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_complete-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-Pininfarina-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_complete-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-Pininfarina-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_complete-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-Pininfarina-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_complete-1536x922.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-Pininfarina-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_complete.jpg 2000w\" /></a><figcaption><em>all c. De Rosa</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>De Rosa collaborated with Italian car designer Pininfarina back in 2019 for their bubbly <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020-de-rosa-sk-pininfarina-aero-road-bike-delivers-new-heart-for-italian-brand/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>san seri</em>f makeove</a>r together with the latest <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020-de-rosa-sk-pininfarina-aero-road-bike-delivers-new-heart-for-italian-brand/\" target=\"_blank\">Super King</a> aero road bike – a design that was already sleekly integrated by modern bike standards. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_Pininfarina-sketch.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_Pininfarina-sketch-800x480.jpg\" alt=\"De Rosa Settanta lightweight carbon aero road bike, design sketch by Pininfarina\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_Pininfarina-sketch-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_Pininfarina-sketch-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_Pininfarina-sketch-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_Pininfarina-sketch-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_Pininfarina-sketch-1536x922.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_Pininfarina-sketch.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>But now the new De Rosa 70 aka Settanta gets a visually lighter aero design that echoes more of their <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/de-rosa-merak-carbon-road-bike-returns-to-pro-racing-with-cofidis-down-under/\" target=\"_blank\">Merak</a> while shedding a lot of frame weight – almost 10% lighter than that lightweight all-rounder and more than 23% lighter than the aero bike!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tech Details</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_frame-details.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_frame-details-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"De Rosa 70 Settanta lightweight carbon aero road bike, designed by Pininfarina, frame\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_frame-details-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_frame-details-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_frame-details-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_frame-details-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_frame-details-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_frame-details-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_frame-details.jpg 1800w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new hi-mod carbon De Rosa 70 road bike features a mix of UD, 1K &amp; 5K fibers, with hints of the carbon weave coming to light in the raw-finished rear end. De Rosa says race-ready stiffness was a main priority for the new frame, but is still managed to drop a claimed two hundred-twenty grams over the four-year-old SK Pininfarina – with the new 70 Pininfarina claimed to weigh just 730g (54cm). </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Even the new fork drops ninety grams, down to a claimed 280g.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_angled-detail.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_angled-detail-800x480.jpg\" alt=\"2023 De Rosa 70 Settanta lightweight carbon aero road bike, designed by Pininfarina, frame detail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_angled-detail-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_angled-detail-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_angled-detail-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_angled-detail-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_angled-detail-1536x922.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_angled-detail.jpg 1800w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new De Rosa 70 maintains edgy motorsports-inspired Pininfarina lines, mixing in flat sides and aerofoil profiles for a balance of looks and aerodynamics. Even with new clearance for up to 32mm tires, De Rosa claims it delivers their lowest drag figures in CFD yet. Up front, the 1.5″ FSA headset is more smoothly integrated than ever, tucked down into the top of the headtube keeping all the cables fully internal for modern electronic shift, hydraulic disc brake groupsets. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_blurred-non-driveside.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_blurred-non-driveside-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"2023 De Rosa 70 Settanta lightweight carbon aero road bike, designed by Pininfarina, non-driveside\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_blurred-non-driveside-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_blurred-non-driveside-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_blurred-non-driveside-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_blurred-non-driveside-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_blurred-non-driveside-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_blurred-non-driveside-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_blurred-non-driveside.jpg 1800w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Overall it keeps the dropped seatstays &amp; proprietary aero seatpost of its predecessors and adopts the ever-so-slightly sloping toptube design of the Merak. A press-fit BB86 sits inside a classic oversized bottom bracket paired to tall sinuous chainstays for drivetrain rigidity, plus flat mount disc brakes and 12mm thru-axles.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_geometry.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_geometry-800x450.jpg\" alt=\"2023 De Rosa 70 Settanta lightweight carbon aero road bike, designed by Pininfarina, geometry\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_geometry-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_geometry-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_geometry-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_geometry-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_geometry-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_geometry-400x225.jpg 400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_geometry-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_geometry.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>2023 De Rosa 70 – Options &amp; availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_head-tube-heart-logo.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_head-tube-heart-logo-800x450.jpg\" alt=\"2023 De Rosa 70 Settanta lightweight carbon aero road bike, designed by Pininfarina, heart logo head tube\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_head-tube-heart-logo-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_head-tube-heart-logo-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_head-tube-heart-logo-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_head-tube-heart-logo-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_head-tube-heart-logo-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_head-tube-heart-logo-400x225.jpg 400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_head-tube-heart-logo-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_head-tube-heart-logo.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new De Rosa 70 / Settanta comes in 8 stock sizes (42.5-56.5cm) and simple white or blue paint jobs. It features the simple modern Pininfarina-design graphics and a special 70th-anniversary <em>Settanta</em> headtube heart logo. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_blue-Dura-Ace.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_blue-Dura-Ace-800x480.jpg\" alt=\"2023 De Rosa 70 Settanta lightweight carbon aero road bike, designed by Pininfarina, blue with Shimano Dura-Ace Di2\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_blue-Dura-Ace-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_blue-Dura-Ace-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_blue-Dura-Ace-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_blue-Dura-Ace-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_blue-Dura-Ace-1536x922.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023-De-Rosa-70-Settanta-lightweight-carbon-aero-road-bike_designed-by-Pininfarina_blue-Dura-Ace.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new bike is available as a complete bike only built up with your choice of premium groupsets – Campagnolo Super Record EPS, Shimano Dura-Ace or Ultegra Di2, or SRAM Red or Force eTap AXS. Wheelsets are matching premium from Campagnolo Hyperon or Bora Ultra WTO, Fulcrum Speed/ Vision SL all wrapped in Vittoria Corsa NEXT tires and topped off with a custom De Rosa 70 Selle Italia or Fizik saddle.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://derosa.it/model/70\" target=\"_blank\">DeRosa.it</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/de-rosa-70-is-a-much-lighter-pininfarina-designed-aero-road-bike/\">De Rosa 70 is a Much-Lighter Pininfarina-designed Aero Road Bike</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"51780100107df3d7744bf91292c35d692debe1885448c2f21a4d5957cc356c2e","category":"Cycling"}